02:04.482 --> 02:06.486
WHY DON'T YOU CHAT ABOUT WHO
YOUR HUSBANDS ARE FUCKING?

02:06.520 --> 02:09.258
OH, LOOK,
HERE COME THE GIRLS.

02:09.291 --> 02:11.029
YOU TAKE CARE, NANCY.

02:11.062 --> 02:13.567
IT MUST BE SO HARD FOR YOU,
BEING ALL ALONE.

02:13.601 --> 02:15.137
GOD BLESS.

02:15.938 --> 02:18.043
MOM?

02:18.076 --> 02:21.049
