UP AFTER SCHOOL.

02:21.082 --> 02:24.221
YES, WELL, SURPRISE.

02:24.255 --> 02:27.662
BLANCA HAD TO TAKE YOUR SISTER
TO THE AIRPORT.

02:27.696 --> 02:29.098
THE AIRPORT?
YEAH.

02:29.131 --> 02:30.702
WHERE'S SHE GOING?

02:30.735 --> 02:35.945
UH, QUINN IS ON HER WAY
TO BOARDING SCHOOL IN MEXICO.

02:35.978 --> 02:37.147
