02:37.181 --> 02:39.018
YEAH, WELL, NOT
A SENTIMENTALIST, YOUR SISTER.

02:39.051 --> 02:40.788
CAN WE TALK ABOUT THIS
IN THE CAR?

02:40.822 --> 02:41.924
