I'LL MEET YOU AT THE DESK.

02:44.863 --> 02:46.633
GO ON.

02:46.667 --> 02:48.904
Nancy: MR. ST. DENIS,
SO NICE TO SEE YOU.

02:48.938 --> 02:50.975
