STRAIGHTEN EVERYTHING OUT.

03:07.374 --> 03:08.978
GO BACK TO CLASS.
I GOT TO PEE.

03:09.011 --> 03:10.313
FINE, HURRY UP.
HOLD UP THE BELT.

03:10.347 --> 03:12.652
REMEMBER TO HOLD UP THE BELT
SO IT DOESN'T GET WET.

03:12.685 --> 03:13.854
Shane: MOM...

03:13.888 --> 03:15.958
HEY, NANCY.
HI, CELIA.

03:21.670 --> 03:24.041
