AT MY FACE?

03:29.418 --> 03:30.922
IT'S CALLED
A "ROOMERANG."

03:30.955 --> 03:32.892
AND WHEN YOU THROW IT ‐‐
WHOOPS ‐‐

03:32.926 --> 03:34.428
