DOESN'T GET IN THE WAY.

03:36.834 --> 03:38.738
BUT I'M NOT SAYING
YOU DID THAT ON PURPOSE.

03:38.771 --> 03:41.242
CAN I HAVE A TISSUE?
OH, SURE. HERE.

03:41.977 --> 03:44.415
