03:44.448 --> 03:46.887
OH, NO. NO, NO.
DON'T TELL ME YOU'RE DRY.

03:46.920 --> 03:48.891
I'M NOT DRY, DOUG.
I'M BROKE.

03:48.924 --> 03:50.795
THANK GOD.

03:50.828 --> 03:53.701
