04:02.418 --> 04:04.890
SAY WHAT YOU WILL
ABOUT ME PERSONALLY,

04:04.923 --> 04:06.894
BUT I'M
A GREAT FUCKING CPA.

04:06.927 --> 04:09.699
YOU WON'T LET ME DEPOSIT CASH
IN MY CHECKING ACCOUNT.

04:09.733 --> 04:12.304
I'M RUNNING ALL OVER TOWN,
PAYING MY BILLS WITH CASH.

04:12.337 --> 04:15.043
BECAUSE I CAN'T HAVE
A PAPER TRAIL OF CASH DEPOSITS.

04:15.076 --> 04:16.145
YOU GOT TO TRUST ME
ON THIS.

04:16.179 --> 04:17.715
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO,
SELL MY HOUSE?

04:17.749 --> 04:19.185
HOW ABOUT LUPITA,
YOUR HOUSEKEEPER?

04:19.218 --> 04:20.521
SHE'S LIKE FAMILY.

04:20.555 --> 04:23.861
BESIDES, HER DAUGHTER IS STILL
IN COURT‐REPORTING SCHOOL.

04:23.894 --> 04:26.934
