TO HAVE TO SELL MORE.

04:30.508 --> 04:34.516
NANCY, IT'S THE OLDEST RULE IN
BUSINESS ‐‐ BUY LOW, SELL HIGH.

04:34.549 --> 04:37.154
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOU GET IT?

04:37.187 --> 04:38.524
SELL <i>HIGH.</i>

04:38.557 --> 04:41.964
IF YOU EVER MAKE A BUSINESS
CARD, YOU COULD USE THAT.

04:41.997 --> 04:44.034
DOUG...

04:44.068 --> 04:45.505
OKAY.

04:45.538 --> 04:47.174
ALL RIGHT, LISTEN,
I'VE BEEN WORKING

04:47.207 --> 04:48.911
ON SETTING UP
A SMALL‐BUSINESS LOAN FOR YOU

04:48.944 --> 04:51.249
SO WE CAN HAVE A FRONT
TO LAUNDER MONEY THROUGH.

04:51.282 --> 04:53.486
THIS WAY, YOU CAN REPLENISH
YOUR CHECKING ACCOUNT,

04:53.521 --> 04:55.658
PAY SOME BILLS, AND ‐‐ BOOM ‐‐
BOB'S YOUR UNCLE.

04:55.691 --> 04:57.227
WHAT'S MY LEGITIMATE
SMALL BUSINESS?

04:57.261 --> 04:58.564
I DON'T KNOW.
PICK SOMETHING.

04:58.597 --> 04:59.966
PAPERWORK'S
ALL THE SAME.

05:00.000 --> 05:01.770
JUST LET ME KNOW
WHAT YOU WANT.

05:01.804 --> 05:04.509
COULD MY COVER BUSINESS
BECOME MY REAL BUSINESS?

05:04.543 --> 05:06.747
IN THIS ECONOMY,
SMALL BUSINESS IS FUCKED.

05:06.780 --> 05:09.485
BUT THAT'LL BE GOOD FOR US.
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

05:09.519 --> 05:12.057
JUST PICK SOMETHING
WITH LOW INVENTORY, OKAY?

05:12.090 --> 05:13.493
