05:13.527 --> 05:15.765
NOW, STOP THAT.
EVERYTHING'S GOING TO BE GREAT.

05:15.798 --> 05:18.804
I'M GUARANTEEING YOU SEVEN
CUSTOMERS AT TOMORROW'S GAME.

05:18.838 --> 05:22.010
