05:24.081 --> 05:26.018
HOW ABOUT
A LITTLE CASH UP FRONT?

05:26.052 --> 05:28.489
SURE.

05:30.595 --> 05:32.431
AH, SHIT,
I'M ALL TAPPED OUT.

05:32.464 --> 05:36.205
I'LL HIT THE ATM LATER,
I PROMISE.

05:36.239 --> 05:37.909
NANCE, I'D OFFER
TO WRITE YOU A CHECK,

05:37.942 --> 05:40.480
BUT THAT SEEMS INSENSITIVE,
NOT TO MENTION UNWISE,

05:40.515 --> 05:42.184
BECAUSE IF
YOU SHOULD GET CAUGHT,

05:42.217 --> 05:44.421
I CAN'T HAVE IT
COMING BACK TO ME.

05:44.455 --> 05:46.425
Nancy: SILAS!

05:46.459 --> 05:48.998
IS THERE A PHONE
OFF THE HOOK UPSTAIRS?!

05:49.031 --> 05:50.100
