I DON'T KNOW THE WHOLE STORY.

07:00.975 --> 07:01.843
YOU'RE SORRY?

07:01.877 --> 07:03.948
SHE'S PROBABLY BEEN TRYING
TO CALL ME.

07:03.981 --> 07:05.851
