SUCH A FUCKING MESS.

07:10.861 --> 07:11.797
SILAS.

07:11.830 --> 07:12.999
HI, MISSUS.

07:13.032 --> 07:15.437
HI, LUPITA.
HOW YOU DOING?

07:15.470 --> 07:17.040
I THINK
I HAVE THE MENOPAUSE.

07:17.074 --> 07:20.781
I'M THINKING I AM GOING TO HAVE
ANOTHER BABY, AND I CRY,

07:20.815 --> 07:23.587
