BROKE AND STINKING OF MARIJUANA.

17:39.317 --> 17:41.789
GUESS THAT'S BETTER
THAN ORIENTAL PUSSY.

17:41.823 --> 17:42.858
EXCUSE ME?

17:42.891 --> 17:45.129
OH, COME ON, NANCY,
I KNOW YOU KNOW.

17:45.162 --> 17:46.498
EVERYBODY KNOWS.

17:46.532 --> 17:48.970
