19:02.050 --> 19:03.118
HELLO?!

19:03.152 --> 19:06.491
HEY, LUPITA.
Lupita: <i>HOLA.</i>

19:06.526 --> 19:09.532
YOU HUNGRY?
I CAN WARM UP SOME PASTA.

19:09.565 --> 19:11.536
