[ Chuckling ] YEAH.

19:43.165 --> 19:46.071
DAD MADE IT ALL BETTER.

19:46.104 --> 19:50.914
Nancy: SILAS, HONEY,
WHAT'S GOING ON?

19:50.947 --> 19:52.951
