EVEN BOTHERING TO SAY GOODBYE.

20:14.294 --> 20:17.668
MY WHOLE FUCKING LIFE,
PEOPLE JUST GO AWAY.

20:19.471 --> 20:21.274
[ SIGHS ]
[ THUD ]

20:21.308 --> 20:23.947
Shane: OW! MOM! OH!

20:23.980 --> 20:26.586
OW! OW! OW! OW! OW!

20:26.619 --> 20:28.923
JESUS!

20:28.957 --> 20:31.261
