THE PHONE'S STILL DEAD.

20:36.104 --> 20:38.676
YOU DON'T SAY "FUCKING"
TO YOUR MOTHER.

20:38.710 --> 20:40.614
[ BEEPING ]

20:40.647 --> 20:42.618
Woman: MA'AM?

20:42.651 --> 20:47.460
