21:28.041 --> 21:29.778
WOMAN, YOU ARE LIGHT.

21:29.812 --> 21:32.985
YOU ARE LIGHTER THAN
MICHAEL JACKSON, YOU SO LIGHT.

21:33.018 --> 21:34.087
WHERE IS MY MONEY?

21:34.120 --> 21:35.991
