LAST NIGHT.

21:36.024 --> 21:37.828
OH.

21:37.861 --> 21:39.698
SORRY TO HEAR THAT.

21:39.732 --> 21:41.502
WHERE IS MY MONEY?

21:41.536 --> 21:44.440
I'LL GET IT, I SWEAR.
I NEED MORE INVENTORY.

21:44.474 --> 21:46.411
