YOU KNOW, WHEN YOU STOP BEING
CUTE AND CLEAN AND FUNNY AT HOME

24:38.856 --> 24:41.629
AND START SPENDING
AFTERNOONS

24:41.662 --> 24:45.737
WITH YOUR HEAD BURIED
IN THE SNATCH OF THE TENNIS PRO,

24:45.770 --> 24:48.442
YEAH, YOU'RE
A PIECE OF SHIT.

24:48.475 --> 24:50.045
ARE YOU GOING
TO DIVORCE HIM?

24:50.079 --> 24:50.847
DIVORCE? [ SCOFFS ]

24:50.880 --> 24:53.619
HE CAN'T SUPPORT
TWO HOUSEHOLDS,

24:53.653 --> 24:57.259
AND I AM NOT LIVING
IN A TOWNHOUSE AGAIN.

24:58.763 --> 25:01.334
SO WHAT DID YOU DO
THAT WAS SO SPECIAL?

25:01.368 --> 25:04.608
I DID EVERYTHING
HE EVER WANTED ‐‐

25:04.641 --> 25:07.714
COSTUMES, ROLE PLAYING.

25:07.748 --> 25:09.551
I BOUGHT
A FUCKING SWING.

25:09.585 --> 25:11.354
LISTEN, MOST GUYS CHEAT...

25:11.388 --> 25:15.429
AND IT'S NOT BECAUSE THE WIFE
IS SOME HORRIBLE, FRIGID BITCH,

25:15.462 --> 25:17.634
BUT IT'S BECAUSE
THEY ALL HAVE

25:17.667 --> 25:20.439
THIS PRIMAL URGE
TO SEEK VARIETY.

25:20.472 --> 25:21.642
PIECES OF SHIT.

25:21.675 --> 25:23.278
DEAN'S A GOOD GUY.

25:23.311 --> 25:24.515
YOU KNOW, SHUT UP.

25:24.548 --> 25:27.053
I'M VERY MAD AT HIM.

25:27.086 --> 25:30.794
HE'S JUST NOT WHAT I THOUGHT
HE'D BE, YOU KNOW.

25:30.827 --> 25:31.862
WHICH WAS?

25:31.896 --> 25:33.833
RICH...

25:33.866 --> 25:35.469
POWERFUL...

25:35.503 --> 25:37.073
FAITHFUL.

25:37.106 --> 25:41.448
HE JUST TURNED OUT TO BE
ANOTHER MID‐LEVEL ASSHOLE.

25:41.481 --> 25:44.287
AND THAT MAKES ME
MRS. MID‐LEVEL ASSHOLE.

25:44.320 --> 25:45.857
THAT'S WHY
I'LL NEVER MARRY.

25:45.890 --> 25:49.531
NO, YOU JUST FUCK THE MARRIED,
AND I HAVE TO WATCH IT ON VIDEO.

25:49.565 --> 25:51.669
NOW I HAVE TO FUCKING DEAL
WITH IT,

25:51.702 --> 25:54.107
AND I DON'T LIKE DEALING
WITH THINGS.

25:54.140 --> 25:58.850
I'D MUCH PREFER TO PRETEND
THEY DON'T EXIST.

25:58.883 --> 26:00.553
I'M SORRY.

26:00.587 --> 26:03.125
YOU'RE A BIG WHORE.

26:05.195 --> 26:06.766
I THINK I SHOULD GO NOW.

26:06.799 --> 26:09.938
OH, SIT YOUR FLAT ASS
BACK DOWN.

26:09.972 --> 26:12.844
YOU KNOW,
YOU'RE A GOOD LISTENER.

26:12.878 --> 26:14.882
THANKS.

26:14.915 --> 26:16.151
FUCK YOU.

26:16.184 --> 26:18.188
LET'S GET
ANOTHER ROUND.

26:36.191 --> 26:38.629
HEY, NANCY!

26:41.702 --> 26:44.575
WHERE'S YOUR ‐‐
WHERE'S YOUR RING?

26:44.608 --> 26:47.781
MY RING?

26:47.814 --> 26:51.154
YEAH, YOUR PRETTY
LITTLE DIAMOND RING.

26:53.191 --> 26:54.695
IT'S IN THE SHOP.

26:54.728 --> 26:58.636
OH, WELL,
I HOPE THEY CAN FIX IT.

26:58.669 --> 27:02.878
YES, ME TOO, CELIA.

27:02.911 --> 27:04.213
THANKS.

27:04.247 --> 27:05.884
YEAH.

27:24.721 --> 27:25.757
WE CAN FIX THIS.

27:25.790 --> 27:27.861
EVERYTHING'S GOING
TO BE OKAY, BUDDY.

27:27.894 --> 27:30.199
YOU GOT THAT, MOM?
[ Chuckling ] YEAH.

27:30.232 --> 27:32.403
DAD MADE IT ALL ‐‐

27:44.728 --> 27:46.064
[ SIGHS ]

27:46.097 --> 27:47.233
MOM?

27:47.266 --> 27:49.203
YEAH, HONEY,
WHAT IS IT?

27:49.237 --> 27:50.907
WHAT HAPPENED?

27:55.048 --> 27:57.988
I GUESS WHEN YOU FELL,
THE CAMERA GOT SMASHED.

28:00.392 --> 28:02.564
YEAH.

28:02.597 --> 28:04.902
YEAH, I GUESS
THAT'S WHAT HAPPENED.

28:04.935 --> 28:06.137
YEAH.

28:06.170 --> 28:09.243
DON'T WORRY,
WE'LL GET ANOTHER ONE.

28:10.947 --> 28:12.918
OKAY.

28:25.108 --> 28:26.477
AMBIEN?

28:26.512 --> 28:29.551
TAKE THEM.
YOU NEED REST.

28:29.585 --> 28:31.689
WHAT ARE
YOU GOING TO DO?

28:31.722 --> 28:32.824
NOTHING.

28:32.857 --> 28:37.166
REALLY, I'M NOT GOING
TO DO A THING.

28:37.199 --> 28:38.869
UNH‐UNH.

28:38.903 --> 28:42.978
LOOK, I'M GONNA TAKE
ONE MYSELF.

28:49.992 --> 28:52.229
SEE?

28:52.263 --> 28:55.202
Good night.

29:07.594 --> 29:09.898
[ Judah Imitating Darth Vader ]
I AM YOUR FATHER, SHANE.

29:09.932 --> 29:11.735
JOIN ME ON THE DARK SIDE,

29:11.769 --> 29:14.273
AND TOGETHER WE CAN RULE
THE UNIVERSE.

29:14.307 --> 29:15.442
NEVER!

29:15.475 --> 29:17.614
THEN PREPARE TO DIE!

29:17.647 --> 29:18.916
NO!

29:18.950 --> 29:21.287
[ BOTH IMITATING
LIGHTSABERS ]

29:21.321 --> 29:22.222
[ LAUGHS EVILLY ]

29:22.256 --> 29:24.761
Nancy: GET BACK
IN HERE RIGHT NOW.

29:24.795 --> 29:26.431
WE ARE NOT DONE TALKING.

29:26.464 --> 29:30.305
JUST SAY GOOD NIGHT, DAD,
AND SHUT OFF THE CAMERA.

29:32.242 --> 29:33.779
[ Normal voice ]
GOOD NIGHT, DAD.

